race.comment: RISE AT DAWN (11) talented gelding who returns from a let-up with the winkers going on. Gets map favours on the limit after being nailed late when fourth in the LR Five Diamonds over 1800m at Rosehill. This is his pet trip and fitted with a recent 1000m jump out win. Hard to catch. ESTADIO MESTALLA (3) tough miler who gets a better set-up for this. Great ride from the draw when a fighting second in the G3 The Gong over 1600m at Kembla Grange. Can go one better. YORKSHIRE (13) this has been the target race, and he should have the speed to get across from the sticky gate. Has further improvement to come after he bounced back with a determined win over 1500m in the G3 Festival Stakes at Rosehill. Gets his chance but his current price looks skinny. ROBUSTO (4) set to peak third-up and won't know himself with the 54kg. Has a solid set of figures over this track and trip and maps to stalk the speed. SABAJ (20) untapped miler who created a big impression winning the Cranbourne Cup. Respect.
